cc:Work.dc:title: CentOS Web Customization
cc:Work.dc:description: This artwork illustrates CentOS web customization. The whole visual style of CentOS web is controlled by header-bg-top.png, header-bg-app.png, footer-bg-app.png images and CSS definition.
